Package org.corfudb.runtime.entries

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IBundleEntry
    This is a bundle entry interface, which is encountered inside the move entries of remotely bundled logs.
    IPayload
    This class represents entries which have a payload.
    IStreamEntry
    This interface represents the minimal functions that a stream entry must support.
